{"tid":658395,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"行山友執到電話被誤作賊 嬲到放返上山","createTime":"2018-05-09T02:39:33.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-09T05:25:37.000Z","uid":130626,"like":3,"dislike":34,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"4549b60d6e95ba97b372dec28d344d5c12378696","tid":658395,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-09T02:39:33.000Z","msg":"好心著雷劈？有網民行青山時執到部iPhone 8，反被事主女朋友當賊同破口大罵。<br />\n <br />\n有網民喺討論區貼文，話行山時執到部iPhone 8:<br />\n<br />\n部機冇電，聯絡唔到機主，<br />\n於時佢帶埋部電話行落山，打算去警署報案。<br />\n <br />\n落山後呢名行山友去咗龍門居食飯，<br />\n並喺餐廳充電，<br />\n到個電話開得返後20分鐘，<br />\n就收到事主女朋友打嚟：<br />\n「你係咪偷左我男朋友部手機 仲要熄埋機？我有gps可以跟蹤你 你唔好諗住可以走得甩 」<br />\n <br />\n行山友畀人當賊扮，非常之嬲咁回應：<br />\n「喂 小姐 我係山上執到部手機 咁部手機冇電我可以點？」<br />\n <br />\n給果行山友畀事主女朋友講粗口鬧咗一輪，<br />\n認為行山友係賊，更表明已報警。<br />\n <br />\n最終行山友話將部電話放返上山！！！<br />\n <br />\n呢件事引嚟好多網民討論，<br />\n有人批評行山友掛住去食飯，<br />\n又有人話香港地好人難做。<br />\n <br />\n大家又覺得邊個有理呢？<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/ZEjrivzANbS6Qu3NqPzYOw--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9MTAyNDtoPTQ2MQ--/http://media.zenfs.com/zh-Hant-HK/homerun/dailytopshare.tumblr.com/872852128da9283818c6366200cf5238\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FZEjrivzANbS6Qu3NqPzYOw--%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9MTAyNDtoPTQ2MQ--%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fzh-Hant-HK%2Fhomerun%2Fdailytopshare.tumblr.com%2F872852128da9283818c6366200cf5238&h=b2068d3d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E8%A1%8C%E5%B1%B1%E5%8F%8B%E5%9F%B7%E5%88%B0%E9%9B%BB%E8%A9%B1%E8%A2%AB%E8%AA%A4%E4%BD%9C%E8%B3%8A-%E5%AC%B2%E5%88%B0%E6%94%BE%E8%BF%94%E4%B8%8A%E5%B1%B1-084915214.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.yahoo.com%2F%25E8%25A1%258C%25E5%25B1%25B1%25E5%258F%258B%25E5%259F%25B7%25E5%2588%25B0%25E9%259B%25BB%25E8%25A9%25B1%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E8%25AA%25A4%25E4%25BD%259C%25E8%25B3%258A-%25E5%25AC%25B2%25E5%2588%25B0%25E6%2594%25BE%25E8%25BF%2594%25E4%25B8%258A%25E5